Capture or restore working-directory snapshots (Sprint 5 §8)

Usage: snapshot <COMMAND>

Commands:
  save     Capture the live working-directory state under a label
  list     List every retained snapshot (id, label, file count, size)
  status   Print one snapshot's full record
  restore  Restore the working directory from a captured snapshot. Requires
           `cap:checkpoint:rollback`
  remove   Drop a snapshot from the store
  help     Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help
          Print help
